Value: Get $300 off select smartphones when you add a new line with DPP.   

Requirements: Eligible on smartphones with a retail value greater than $300.  Excludes upgrades. New line required. Applied as bill credit over applicable DPP term.  Available on all price plans that are eligible to add a line.   

This promotion allows customers to add the smartphone of their choice. 


Source: RTD

Value: Get $150 off any new iPad Tablet via recurring BIC over applicable DPP term when you add with device payment. Bill credit will start to appear on customer bill in 1-2 bill cycles.

Requirements: Must add a new iPad Tablet with device payment. Cannot be combined with other equipment discounts. Promo credit ends when balance paid or line terminated/transferred. Promo only stacks with trade-in promos and buy device of BOGO(HO) promos.

This is one of the the richest iPad tablet promotions in market. It does not require device bundling, trade-in or specific price plan. Simply add an iPad to your plan and save $150.
